channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: Oscar Mayer Wienermobile Crashes Along Chicago Area Highway
item.description: The hot dog-shaped vehicle hit a car Monday morning and its driver lost control and overcorrected, causing it to roll onto its side on I-294.

item.title: Woman, 70, charged after baby girl killed by car crashing into pram outside hospital
item.description: Bridget Carole Curtis, 70, has been charged with causing death by dangerous driving. Mabli Cariad Hall died after being struck while in her pram outside a hospital in Wales

item.title: Sharks ‘high on cocaine’ after drugs are being flushed down the loo
item.description: It could be affecting their behaviour making them more aggressive.

item.title: Jay Slater latest as friend answers six burning questions - from Rolex to rumoured 'fight'
item.description: Ayub Qassim, who brought Jay Slater back to a remote Airbnb after they partied together in Tenerife, has answered six burning questions surrounding the teenager's tragic death

item.title: Psychic who envisioned Trump assassination attempt gives his US election prediction
item.description: 'I wasn't expecting this to happen until at least August this year.'

item.title: Tomato storage hack keeps fruit fresh for up to 10 days - and you only need one item
item.description: Tomatoes are a kitchen staple for a reason, but it's important to keep them under the right conditions if you want to extend their lifespan and enjoy their freshness for longer.

item.title: 14 children end up in hospital after trying ‘adult only’ crisps
item.description: The 'R18' crisps are made using an extract from the ultra-spicy ghost pepper.

item.title: French airport evacuated for 'security reasons' after arson attack on rail network
item.description: The Basel-Mulhouse airport, located at the Swiss-French border, has been evacuated for security reasons, hours after a a 'massive, coordinated arson attack' disrupted France's rail network

item.title: Woman describes out of body aura she felt in near-death experience after crash
item.description: 'The experience has allowed me to see the beauty of life.'

item.title: Ed Sheeran's brutal four word response when asked if Prince Harry is a pal
item.description: Ed Sheeran has come face to face with Prince Harry more than once over the years but it's unknown how close the pair really are
